estingly, Double Dragon 2 has a vertical mirroring for it's intro/title screen, but horizontal mirroring for everything else.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">ca65 delegates placement of code in the binary image to the linker.</div>
<br />I see. All this makes me wonder what nbasic is programmed to do...</div>

